<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 07 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="7" arg="0x1010 0x1100 0xcd00" /></message>
	<message label="016" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />在這種天氣
進行訓練的時候<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就會讓人很想學學看<delay8 />
棒球選手在大雨之中，<delay8 />
滿身泥濘的帥氣模樣啊──！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="017" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Angry" target="actor" targetSpec="" />即使是下雨天，也是可以進行訓練的喔！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />比方說可以去計算落下來的雨滴數量，<delay8 />
來訓練你的<delay8 />動態視力啊！<pageBreak /><anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />7、<delay20 />8、<delay20 />9<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Frantic" target="actor" targetSpec="" />數不清啊！！<delay8 />太多了！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="018" attrib="00 00 00 09 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />職業選手的訓練，<delay8 />
是不會受天氣變化影響的喔！<pageBreak /><anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" />所以就算是這種下雪天，<delay8 />
我也還是會持續訓練的！<delay frames="40" />
<colour id="4" />……雖然我覺得有點冷就是了，<tag a="110" b="6" />。<colour id="65535" /></message>
	<message label="019" attrib="00 00 00 0a 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Angry" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你聽好囉──！<delay20 />真正的職業選手，
即使在這種下大雪的日子，<delay20 />
也依然會持續地<delay8 />鍛鍊自己！<pageBreak /><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay20 />雖然我不是職業選手，<delay8 />
<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但我也會鍛鍊自己的！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="020" attrib="00 00 00 05 00 00 00 00"><anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />像今天<delay8 />這樣的好天氣，<delay frames="40" />
就會讓人心血來潮地<delay8 />
想要練<tag a="135" b="6" arg="0xcd00" />耶──！<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過<delay20 />只要能夠活動身體，<delay8 />
<anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />其實不管做什麼運動，<delay8 />
我都很喜歡喔！<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="021" attrib="00 00 00 06 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Angry" target="actor" targetSpec="" />總覺得這種氣氛，<delay20 />
就像等一下<delay8 />最終魔王會出現一樣耶……<pageBreak /><anim id="TakenAback" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="0" />！<delay20 />
該不會<delay8 />你就是大魔王吧！？<10_4 />
<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哈哈，<delay8 />不可能吧──！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="022" attrib="00 00 00 0b 00 00 00 00"><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />看到花瓣在空中飛舞的樣子<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
就覺得自己<delay8 />好像置身在
勝利大遊行的隊伍裡耶<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="HappyFlower" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="33" />！謝謝你們──！<delay20 />
以後也請各位繼續支持<delay8 />
<tag a="135" b="6" arg="0xcd00" />界的<delay8 /><tag a="110" b="10" />喔──！<pageBreak /><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就像這樣！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這意象訓練<delay8 /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />
真是太完美啦！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="023" attrib="18 00 00 01 00 0a 00 00"><anim id="Angry" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你聽好囉！<delay20 />健身可是不分天氣好壞的。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />最重要的<delay20 />是每天都踏踏實實地<delay frames="30" />
培育你的肌肉！</message>
	<message label="024" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="024_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />順便告訴你，<delay20 />天氣好的時候，<delay8 />
我都會去外面慢跑，<delay20 />天氣糟的時候，<delay8 />
我都會在房間裡做深蹲喔──！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="024_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />總之對我來說，<delay8 />
不管天氣怎麼樣，不管我人在哪裡，<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />只要能活動身體就好啦！<delay20 /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="5" />。</message>
	<message label="024_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />吸收充足的陽光，<delay20 />
還有雨水就能夠成長茁壯<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="Shocked" target="actor" targetSpec="" />啊！<delay frames="40" /><anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />結果<delay8 />聊到植物去了！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="025" attrib="1a 00 00 05 00 09 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />嘿嘿，<delay20 />雖然現在是晚上，<delay frames="30" />
但看得見星星，還是挺亮的嘛──！</message>
	<message label="026" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="026_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">像今天這樣<delay8 />舒適的晚上，<delay20 />
<anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />讓我忍不住想跑到水平線的盡頭耶──！<delay frames="40" />
<colour id="4" />咦？<delay20 />地平線<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />是在哪裡啊？<tag a="110" b="6" />。<colour id="65535" /></message>
	<message label="026_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">我問你，<delay20 /><anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你有數過天上的星星嗎？<delay frames="50" />
<anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我每次抬頭數到100以後，<delay20 />
<anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />都會因為脖子痛而放棄<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="026_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />在星光照耀下的肌肉，<delay20 />
看起來比早上還要線條分明，<delay20 />
<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />所以<delay8 />我特別喜歡喔，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="101" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今天的天氣真是舒適啊──！<10_4 />
<anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />要是好天氣可以持續到晚上的話，<delay20 />
一定可以看得到燦爛的星星──！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="102" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今天的天氣很好耶──！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />照這樣下去，<delay8 />等到了晚上，
說不定看得到流星喔！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="103" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="1" arg="0xc9 0xca 0xcb" /></message>
	<message label="104" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="3" />，<delay20 />你快看！
有彩虹耶──！<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />看起來<delay8 />就像是空中<delay8 />
出現了一座大橋一樣──！<pageBreak /><anim id="HappyFlower" target="actor" targetSpec="" />好！<delay8 />我要朝著那座橋的方向，<delay8 />
全力衝刺過去啦！！<delay frames="40" />
你也來跟我一起衝吧──！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="105" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />喂！<delay8 />你快看──！<delay20 />
出現兩道彩虹了耶──！<tag a="110" b="6" />。<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這種日子啊，<delay20 />
一定會有好事發生！<delay frames="40" />
比方說<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 /><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />腹肌會變成六塊之類的！<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="106" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />像今天這樣雖然很冷，<delay8 />卻又沒什麼雲的日子，<delay20 />
說不定看得到極光喔──！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="107" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="3" />！<delay20 />
你看到極光了嗎？<pageBreak /><anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />感覺就像是一場天文秀，太驚人了──！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我真的<delay8 />覺得好感動喔！<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="5" />。</message>
	<message label="108" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你……<delay20 />是<tag a="110" b="3" />吧？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哈哈，<delay8 />因為濃霧讓我看不太清楚，<delay20 />
所以想確認一下是誰啦！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="109" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這雨下得真大！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />再加上<delay8 />隆隆作響的雷聲，<delay20 />
我只要趁現在大喊就不會被罵了！<pageBreak /><tag a="10" b="12" /><anim id="Cheering" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay20 /><10_10 /><size value="150" />啊────！！！！<size value="100" /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><10_9 /></message>
	<message label="201" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你快看──！<delay8 />
天上有星星掉下來了耶──！<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />嘿嘿，<delay8 />這景象很美吧？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過，<delay8 />那些星星最後
到底會跑去哪裡啊？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="202" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />有傳聞說，<delay20 />只要用<colour id="1" />操控搖桿<colour id="65535" />抬頭看天空，<delay8 />
同時對著流星按下<colour id="1" /><colour id="65535" />許願，<delay20 />
願望就會實現喔──！<delay8 />你知道嗎？<pageBreak /><anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過要在流星消失前許完願，<delay8 />
難度還挺高的吧？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="IdeaBulb" target="actor" targetSpec="" />啊，<delay8 />只要許簡短一點的願望就可以了吧！<pageBreak /><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />簡短一點<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay8 />呃……<delay8 />呃……<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Frantic" target="actor" targetSpec="" />結果<delay8 />我還是只來得及<delay8 />
講出「呃」而已啊！！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="203" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我現在正在數<delay20 />
天上掉下來的星星<delay8 />有幾顆！<pageBreak /><anim id="Angry" target="actor" targetSpec="" />像這樣集中精神去數的話，<delay8 />
就能鍛鍊到動態視力！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />也能欣賞流星，<delay8 />真是一石二鳥啊！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
</msbt>